    "This proposal analyzes the limitations and capabilities of six AI chatbots in scholarly writing in archaeology and humanities.",
    "The analysis focuses on quantitative accuracy and qualitative precision, with ChatGPT-4 scoring near the passing grade.",
    "All AI chatbots, with the exception of ChatGPT-4, have demonstrated competence in the reunification of existing knowledge, but have not generated original scientific content.",
    "The study suggests that large language models have reached a plateau, and while AI chatbots have revolutionized subject generation of ability to create original scientific contributions remains limited [10].",
    "ChatGPT has revolutionized writing, but it's crucial to differentiate human writing from AI."
